Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:31.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Did you know? Did you Know? Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.51,0:24:35.90,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,There's a baby koala in the eucalyptus tree
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:40.53,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Looking for its mother from branch to branch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.81,0:24:45.24,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,It gathers plenty of leaves to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.56,0:24:50.00,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,And naps in the cradle of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.99,0:25:04.22,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Did you know? Did you know? Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.50,0:25:08.93,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The kookaburra is playing by the river
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.25,0:25:13.60,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,It's always so merry, so merry
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.92,0:25:18.32,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Uhahahaha wuhahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.07,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Even if mischievous wuhahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.35,0:25:28.33,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to show you, I want to show you the forest animals
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.61,0:25:33.54,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to show them to you
